ðŸ”¹ Hooks kya hote hain?
Hooks basically functions hote hain jo React ke features ko directly access karne dete hain jaise:
state (useState)
lifecycle methods (useEffect)
context (useContext)
ref (useRef)
aur bhi custom hooks




âš¡ Important Points:
useState ek hi value handle karta hai (string, number, object, array, etc.).
Agar tum multiple values chahte ho, to multiple useState() calls kar sakte ho.
State update asynchronous hota hai (thoda delay ho sakta hai).
React automatically UI ko re-render karta hai jab state change hoti hai.





































